{"tid":176504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"收鬼機案　蘋果前員工判社服","createTime":"2017-03-28T08:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T09:20:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb83d502827a246bffe2ded58649a1bb445f6e30","tid":176504,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:27:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19972259&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170328\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19972259%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170328&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0V0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9f630260\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19972259%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170328&h=d7357b81\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19972259&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170328</a><br />\n<br />\n收鬼機案　蘋果前員工判社服<br />\n<br />\n法庭&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n被告張悅海（右）昨在友人護送下離庭。歐陽聯發攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】蘋果公司前員工利用公司購物14天內可退款的政策，以每部約千元報酬，利誘在職舊同事充當內鬼，回收包裝完好、但內部零件已遭更換的iPhone「鬼機」。前員工早前在九龍城法院被裁定行賄罪成，昨被判100小時社會服務令。<br />\n被告張悅海（27歲）於前年11月5日賄賂蘋果亞洲有限公司男員工區卓偉，審訊時指區主動要求他提供「鬼機」，但遭裁判官斥責「一派胡言」。辯方昨呈上被告家人所撰求情信，指被告誠實可靠，又指蘋果沒有損失，請求輕判。裁判官最終接納報告意見，判處社服令。被告在散庭後立即更換衣服，在友人掩護下跑上私家車離開。<br />\n案件編號：KCCC4007/16<br />\n■記者歐陽聯發"},{"pid":"17e5a8d957bc34e4fe13aab0539b53334ccdbb3e","tid":176504,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:28:45.000Z","msg":"誠實可靠？蘋果冇損失？"},{"pid":"affafb8e1afb780ff3b57b4d949231d6f8f11843","tid":176504,"uid":94720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T09:10:37.000Z","msg":"點解佢同事無比人拉？🤔"},{"pid":"d9666fc05f9a676048fb6a5a10675e3ed73f1ec1","tid":176504,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T09:20:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>誠實可靠？蘋果冇損失？</blockquote><br />\n屌你老味,呢d理由全部都係加監既理由黎<br />\n死得臨頭都仲講大話"}]}